First released in 2003, the Nike Air Zoom Spiridon Cage 2 is as relevant today as it was back in the day. Featuring original design lines and a caged Air Zoom unit, it gives you a responsive ride with early-2000s style.

Colour Shown: Light Sandstone/Cardinal Red/Black/Metallic Silver
Style: CJ1288-001
Country/Region of Origin: Vietnam

Name: Nike Cortez Leather SE
Description:
The revamped Cortez maintains the retro appeal you know and love with a wider toe area and firmer side panels, so you can comfortably wear them all day without any warping. This version is crafted with full-grain leather, which is thick and durable. A fold-over tongue adds to its retro aesthetic.

Colour Shown: Parachute Beige/Off-Noir/Gum Dark Brown/Parachute Beige
Style: IM8057-297
Country/Region of Origin: Indonesia

Name: Tatum 3 PF
Description:
Made for movers and shakers, the Tatum 3 offers a contouring fit in a lightweight design, helping you dominate the game in the smoothest of fashion. Sound familiar? A strong but flexible upper gives you the containment and stretch that quick cuts and dynamic movements demand. So, whether you're breaking records or ankles, you can shift in and out of action just like the champ himself. No pressure.

Colour Shown: White/White/Black
Style: HQ5041-101
Country/Region of Origin: Vietnam
